00:17:46.403 --> 00:17:48.403
♪Kisah kita terletak di pegunungan♪

00:17:48.500 --> 00:17:52.575
♪Seperti lukisan abadi yang dilukis dengan tinta♪

00:17:52.975 --> 00:17:54.700
♪Tempat di mana bunga berguguran♪

00:17:54.738 --> 00:17:58.723
♪Aku senang aroma
